data.description: Cozy single story home highlighting multiple upgrades. New luxury vinyl plank and tile floors are a breeze to maintain while the bedrooms and living spaces have fresh new carpet. A spacious kitchen showcases stainless steel appliances, granite counters, new backsplash, a kitchen island, and an under-mount sink. Both formal dining and breakfast rooms are flooded with natural light. Outdoors is an open patio, wooden fence, and a community pool perfect for summer. Move-in ready.
